{"tid":2297222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平價羽毛球拍奪命 一揮即斷 場邊12歲童遭拍桿穿眼插腦亡","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T06:34:26.000Z","uid":200550,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e308bc50860c9eea79160282d447a48e3ad15adb","tid":2297222,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"湖南郴州本月1日發生一宗離奇的劣質羽毛球拍命案！一塊羽毛球被揮動時突然柄桿分離，中桿插中場邊一名12歲男童小雷，導致其顱腦嚴重受傷，出現顱內出血、腦腫脹，一星期後不治。小雷的父親打算向商家、廠家和學校追究責任。球拍製造商未正面回應事件，僅稱「事情搞好了你們就會知道了」。<br />\n<br />\n小雷所讀中學的報告顯示，小雷1日與同學在校內超市花了25元（約30港元）購買了兩副共4塊羽毛球拍後，到操場打球，小雷下場休息，其他同學繼續在場上拍球，未料其中一塊新買的羽毛球拍突然斷裂，柄桿分離，拍身桿部猛然飛脫插中小雷的右眼，傷及顱腦，小雷隨即被送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n剩低嘅自己入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201122/SHUU66UGWNCX3MTHOKRLCDI5TI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201122%2FSHUU66UGWNCX3MTHOKRLCDI5TI%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=9f411fce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201122%2FSHUU66UGWNCX3MTHOKRLCDI5TI%2F&h=347482db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201122/SHUU66UGWNCX3MTHOKRLCDI5TI/</a>"},{"pid":"6bb91cce3c7e4e69ee1da14b377a443d2c7ebe90","tid":2297222,"uid":200550,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfJmVWK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfJmVWK.gif&h=6eecd66a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65b20b55b9e09ff7366b25a6083f070faeddf284","tid":2297222,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"新網球王子中國真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ab9a37668946464d27d96a29365809ecec297b","tid":2297222,"uid":200550,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b20b55b9e09ff7366b25a6083f070f